{"tid":686614,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先可以阻止我爸俾零用錢我","createTime":"2018-06-01T12:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-01T13:09:58.000Z","uid":40847,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"68579a73b072f76f2da2780f249961c278c86406","tid":686614,"uid":40847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:24:54.000Z","msg":"屋企唔係有錢，<br />\n呀爸做嘢辛苦，但每個月都堅持俾一千零用我。<br />\n得閒又問我夠唔夠錢洗，唔夠又塞幾舊嚟。<br />\n本身我仲爭佢萬幾蚊，依家做緊parttime，未還。<br />\n頭先又塞零用俾我，我已經不停拒絕，但佢好瀟灑咁話：「唔駛啦！袋住佢！」然後轉身坐低，並不帶走一片雲彩......<br />\n<br />\n唉！有啲心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 60歲人仲做勞動緊自己個身體，放工返嚟成日話手痛腳痛，佢之前做過大手術，兩隻腳都冇咗條骨....留返啲錢自己洗好過啦，真係唔駛理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老豆 我愛你 希望我大個可以賺好多錢俾你洗"},{"pid":"db06f2dc674dbfb2ff316acae891484b403b4aca","tid":686614,"uid":124256,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d1fc4f232ce2d3342a560432ac512c73efa255","tid":686614,"uid":20143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:27:15.000Z","msg":"辣撒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637068d4c70713ffc9598ee59ec120ccfea01d62","tid":686614,"uid":174125,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:28:44.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係咁做 但我會開個戶口幫佢存住先 有咩急事就有一d錢應急"},{"pid":"6b3ca0f4a4e82e486a9fc44d06b4ce4065863b60","tid":686614,"uid":78971,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:29:56.000Z","msg":"好撚嘔心"},{"pid":"e10ac116c69381b9f0565e3b506e1fb7ce3441f9","tid":686614,"uid":89801,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:30:43.000Z","msg":"佢比左你 你就要洗？<br />\n你唔識暗中放返係佢銀包？<br />\n得把口講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc90725347dbabf53349fd88036a013eef8516cb"